CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 27, 1962, pg. 13 reads: "Good Luck - C.E. Askew (left) is shown making a presentation to retiring board chairman Mike Robbe, as Lester Blynn observes at the affair at the Homewood YMCA. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of C.E. Askew presenting plaque to retiring board chairman Mike Robbe, as Lester Blynn looks on, standing in Homewood YMCA
